snippet.title: Monkey See Monkey Doo Doo VR - Official App Lab Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Monkey See Monkey Doo Doo VR Launches January 31st for App Lab! 

Download on AppLab: http://monkeydoovr.com/play

Visit our Website: http://monkeydoovr.com
Join the Discord: http://monkeydoovr.com/discord
Follow our TikTok: http://monkeydoovr.com/tiktok
Download the press kit: http://monkeydoovr.com/presskit

Swing through the floating jungles of the Bermuda Triangle as you race against other players to collect bananas to trade for the hottest monkey merch. Fling doo doo at other players to steal their bananas and send them plummeting to the hungry croc below. Be prepared to break a sweat in this fast-paced, multiplayer adventure!
